## 2. OpenCode Server (:4096)

API REST completa para controle programatico:
- `POST /session` — criar sessao
- `POST /session/:id/message` — enviar prompt
- `GET /session/:id/message` — listar mensagens
- `GET /mcp` — status MCP servers
- `POST /mcp` — adicionar MCP dinamicamente
- `GET /event` — SSE event stream
- `GET /find?pattern=` — busca em arquivos

### Uso no NeoCortex
- nc-guardian → validar via `/session/:id/message`
- nc-auditor → auditar via `/session` + `/find`
- nc-courier → executar via `/session/:id/shell`
- Monitoramento → `/event` SSE stream





